  <entry>
    <title>Flarum论坛插件推荐（亲测可用，截至V1.7.2）</title>
    <url>/2023/04/10/06/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<div class="note-large blue"><div class="notel-title"><p>前言</p>
</div><div class="notel-content"><p>本文中提及的插件大部分为博主自建论坛所用，会额外推荐其他插件。这些可能与您的需求不一致，您可以前往<a class="link"   href="https://discuss.flarum.org.cn/" >Flarum中文社区 <i class="fa-regular fa-arrow-up-right-from-square fa-sm"></i></a>、<a class="link"   href="https://discuss.flarum.org/" >Flarum官方英文社区 <i class="fa-regular fa-arrow-up-right-from-square fa-sm"></i></a>、<a class="link"   href="https://extiverse.com/" >extiverse插件展示站 <i class="fa-regular fa-arrow-up-right-from-square fa-sm"></i></a> 等寻找更多插件。<br>以下插件均经博主实测可正常运行（博主的运行环境：CentOS 7.9，Flarum V1.7.2，PHP 8.1）</p>
</div></div>

<div class="note warning"><p>使用安装插件命令前，请务必确保已处于站点文件目录</p>
</div>



<p><strong>0. 清除缓存（插件安装或配置后最好通过以下命令清除缓存以减少意外bug等的发生）</strong></p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Php"><figure class="iseeu highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">php flarum cache:clear</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<h2 id="一、帖子编辑、发布等"><a href="#一、帖子编辑、发布等" class="headerlink" title="一、帖子编辑、发布等"></a>一、帖子编辑、发布等</h2><ol>
<li><p>在帖子中插入 Font Awesome 图标</p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Php"><figure class="iseeu highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">composer <span class="keyword">require</span> antoinefr/flarum-ext-bbcode-fa</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
</li>
<li><p>发布时预览</p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Php"><figure class="iseeu highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">composer <span class="keyword">require</span> zerosonesfun/composer-preview</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
</li>
<li><p>显示帖子的修改记录</p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Php"><figure class="iseeu highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">composer <span class="keyword">require</span> the-turk/flarum-diff</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
</li>
<li><p>帖子内投票</p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Php"><figure class="iseeu highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">composer <span class="keyword">require</span> fof/polls</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
</li>
<li><p>自动识别并实时显示图片、视频链接</p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Php"><figure class="iseeu highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">composer <span class="keyword">require</span> fof/formatting</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></li>
</ol>
<h2 id="二、显示、美化"><a href="#二、显示、美化" class="headerlink" title="二、显示、美化"></a>二、显示、美化</h2><ol>
<li><p>简体中文语言包</p>
<div class="highlight-container" data-rel="Php"><figure class="iseeu highlight php"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">composer <span class="keyword">require</span> flarum-lang/chinese-simplified</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
</li>
<li><p>实现网页帖子实时刷新（推荐论坛达到一定用户体量时采用）</p>
